text: David Souto (; born 26 March 1992 in Caracas) is a Venezuelan tennis player. Souto has a career high ATP singles ranking of 208 achieved on 21 April 2014. He also has a career high ATP doubles ranking of 307 achieved on 28 April 2014. In juniors, Souto has a career high combined ranking of 10 achieved in 2009.
